Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.57,0:00:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.20,0:00:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, let's go, let's go, Jouka!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.45,0:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awesome, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.05,0:00:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The barrier between the girls' and boys'\Nbuildings gets lifted just once a year—
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.96,0:01:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,during the big sports festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.04,0:01:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then... {?? maybe koshite}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.16,0:01:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori, want a burger? \NMaybe a donut? Or udon?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.89,0:01:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.77,0:01:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Udon today. I'm starving.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yuki agrees! {usually I'd ignore 3rd person but this episode is yuki's 20 minutes in the spotlight and talking about herself in 3rd person is her shtick to make her seem more childish so the translation feels incomplete without it}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.22,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.82,0:01:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We Spring Team girls \Nare on decoration duty today. {idk what this harugumi group is}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.58,0:01:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work. {implying "then you won't be going with us to eat"}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.18,0:01:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can help ourselves \Nto your portion, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.43,0:01:54.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm totally late, and in this crowd too. \NYuki's got no luck at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.05,0:01:55.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.49,0:02:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorance is bliss—\Nespecially for teachers. {stretch but she means "none of the teachers know, and that's why it works"}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.23,0:02:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.08,0:02:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good for your eyes—or ears.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.18,0:02:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.80,0:02:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, once a year, on the sports festival day, the boys and girls who are usually kept apart
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.81,0:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,end up having their own little “festival” \Nin the shadow of all the excitement on the field.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyaa! I had no idea. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.45,0:02:32.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,Those thrilling little adventures only happen \Nif you've got the right guy, though... {a boyfriend}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.33,0:02:37.16,Thought,,0,0,0,,If only Yuki had a wonderful boyfriend too...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,No, we'd probably do something even bolder.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh my god, you pervert! \NWhat on earth is Yuki thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.08,0:03:01.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,A­... A molester! {chikan}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.25,0:03:08.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,I... I can't speak... I can't move!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.47,0:03:09.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.93,0:03:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Molester! A molester!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell! {????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.32,0:03:30.00,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.13,0:03:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not me! I swear!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not him!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wrong guy? \NDamn, so it's not him?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{Guess we erred. \NNothing to see here.} {let's go back or something} Aw, rats. Let's skedaddle, boys.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.66,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.75,0:03:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. This is my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.76,0:03:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. It's fine. \NJust go home already.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. 
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.27,0:04:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{Aren't you clingy?!}You're damn clingy, ain'tcha?!\NLook, I said it's not a serious injury, so cut it o—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki... Yuki... {I would kill anyone who makes her cry}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.27,0:04:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look, I appreciate you worrying \Nenough to follow me, I really do, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting dark, see? {/late}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.84,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is Yuki's way home.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.83,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.14,0:04:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you saw Satoshi around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.19,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That prick! If he thinks he can run somewhere I can't see, we'll prove him wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him no matter what! Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.49,0:05:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,M-My heart's pounding...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,Is it because a man is touching Yuki? {think mune is just "heart" and she doesn't say that a man is touching her chest}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.88,0:05:15.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez... W-What am I to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they leave?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.88,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.77,0:05:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, bye now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.16,0:05:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm really not in a position \Nto walk you home right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.15,0:05:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cappy! {her trademark phrase, doesn't mean anything in particular so idk what to put here tbh}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.44,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really? \NThat's great, Yuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our chests were pressed together... { like this - showing on her plushie}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.38,0:05:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki's heart was racing!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.29,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what they call first love, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? His name?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki's so stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.41,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{It happened because I only have\N dirty thoughts on my mind!} And it's all my fault for \N only thinking dirty thoughts!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yes, Manami-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.94,0:06:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, I heard from Saori. \NYou're really thoughtless, you know that? {hasty/careless}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.45,0:06:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... But I didn't realize I liked him \Nuntil after we parted.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.45,0:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down and think back carefully, come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say you saw Satoshi around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi... Satoshi...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They called him Satoshi-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.37,0:06:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But his friends looked kind of scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.15,0:06:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... So things are\Nmore complicated than it seems? {lit: a man with an interesting history (story); with a shady history; with circumstances that are difficult to explain}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy goes to Jouka Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was wearing our uniform.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've said that sooner!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.57,0:07:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard! So you've finally gone into heat, huh? \NGood for you. Good— { to rut; to go into heat / hit puberty - if we want to be merciful}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{What kind of way is that to put it?!} Don't talk about her like she's an animal!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.11,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I was just phrasing it differently.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.99,0:07:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say something that tramples \Non a maiden's feelings like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it again and we're through! {breaking off a relationship; permanent breach of friendship; rupture}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.65,0:07:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, Kobayashi, that guy's gotta be \Na transfer student named Kogure Satoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure... Satoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He was absent today.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.63,0:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is it because of yesterday's injuries...? {when other passengers beat him up}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.64,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, apparently he's barely shown up \Nto school since transferring.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's that flashy group \Nlooking for a guy named Satoshi...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like there's something shady going on.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki can't just sit around!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.67,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... Does she really have to go\Nchange clothes for something like this? {going to see satoshi}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she does. {lit: that's necessary}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl's heart is delicate, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.06,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to run away, you know. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.25,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to ask you something, is all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.66,Top,,0,0,0,,Seen this guy? {?? shinai idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.26,0:08:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lying to us will only make it worse.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.07,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like these ladies \Nreally don't know anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.16,0:09:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.66,0:09:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Always take care of your informants!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.91,0:09:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.63,0:09:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the May Queen potato \Nwe carefully cultivated at school! {potato variety}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Help yourselves! {/eat it}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you see this man...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,call us at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.70,0:09:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? That guy they said they're after... {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.18,0:09:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Yuki's first love \Nis turning into a life-or-death matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Cappy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.48,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lovely!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Cappy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.85,0:10:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was freeloading at a relative's place, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.93,0:10:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder we couldn't find \Na nameplate that said “Kogure.”
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.46,0:10:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you'll see me in a better light now, huh? {because he's freeloading too}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.03,0:10:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip! {/you're too spoiled}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.30,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, is nobody home?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's open!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.34,0:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.39,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to thank you properly.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.35,0:11:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kobayashi Yuki, \NClass 2-C at Jouka Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really in high school?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.69,0:11:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were my\Ncousin's elementary school friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.78,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Elementary school...?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, no, actually, it suits you so well!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it! So cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.15,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Cappy!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, how'd you find this place?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a friend of mine happened to know it. {by chance}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Sorry, but I'm kind of busy right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.43,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki can help!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey... Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.55,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of my apology. \NYour room's on the second floor, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.29,0:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Satoshi-san,\Nwhat month were you born?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A-April.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.48,0:11:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at the sports festival, \Nwe'll be on the same Spring Team. Cappy!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.50,0:12:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you're almost finished already? {moving ig?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.22,0:12:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki was all fired up... Too bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,I-Is she clueless or just forward? {??? muboubi - defenceless; unprotected; vulnerable - idk what it means in this case; daitan - bold/daring - essentially just asking if she doesn't know or doesn't care}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But this feels more like moving out than in.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.78,0:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm moving.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You are, Satoshi-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm changing schools.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But you just transferred here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.74,0:12:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! Yuki hates that! \NShe had just found her first love!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,First love?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.53,0:12:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's the one sweet chance each year\Nwhen boys and girls get to be together.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.63,0:12:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A sweet chance?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.80,0:12:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! If Yuki and Satoshi got together, \Nwe might even advance to a first kiss!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.70,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I actually prepared myself \Nto go way farther than that! {to sex}{lit: braced myself for even more bold things}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.03,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! You've prepared yourself, \Nbut what about your partner? {lit: don't just brace yourself on your own - meaning "I have to be prepared too"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.37,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... could you please not transfer \Nuntil after the sports festival?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That sports festival \Nis exactly why I have to transfer.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.88,0:12:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Yuki doesn't get it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.19,0:13:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to the sports festival too! \NI want a girlfriend too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.83,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Norimatsu Kintaro from the Norimatsu Gang is around,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.84,0:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{spring will never come for me \Nat a sports festival!} {literal} the springtime of my youth \N will never blossom!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The people from last night, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.03,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen between you and them?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming for revenge.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.91,0:13:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.30,0:13:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I show up, the sports festival'll \Nfall into total chaos.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.51,0:13:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So transferring is my only option.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.48,0:13:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't help overhearing. \NPlease let us help you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.08,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how relentless those guys are. \NThey just don't give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.80,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jouka has its own way of doing things.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.73,0:13:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really planning to spend your whole life \Nrunning away from sports festivals?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.15,0:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer after transfer...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.58,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I never even managed to make any real friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This means the world... {/I'm so happy}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.05,0:14:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it! My last {high school }sports festival...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.76,0:14:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of first love! {lit: first love sports festival, the final in high school}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.41,0:14:03.36,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Cappy!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You've found out \Nwhere Satoshi's transferred?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, sir. Jouka Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And they've got a big sports festival \Nthe day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.79,0:14:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.77,0:14:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's planning to compete.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too naïve, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.57,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive you \Nfor the incident which changed my life!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.04,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather every member of the Norimatsu Gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going in.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.02,0:14:27.07,Overlap,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can do it!}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.73,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Is there anyone here \Nwith naturally curly hair? {perm hair}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A scavenger hunt? {scavenger hunt race}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.00,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These items are brutal! \NLook at this! {list of things to find}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.29,0:14:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,“Tightly curled hair?!" {curly hair; kinky hair; frizzy hair}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, wait right here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.05,0:15:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A sports festival, huh? Nice stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,Satoshi, you were fast, all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,No matter what you did, you outshone me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.72,Top,,0,0,0,,Satoshi-kun! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.41,0:15:28.20,Top,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.70,0:15:32.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,But... But... But...!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi! Lose, why don'tcha?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! That's sneaky, Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat... {??????? urusai?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! You stink, Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! He pooped his pants!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.57,Overlap,,0,0,0,,It's not true! Shut up! {uso? urusai?}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He totally pooped his pants!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Poopy pants! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.37,0:16:15.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, I've hated sports festivals \Nout of sheer humiliation.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.22,0:16:18.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,So there's no way I'll ever let you \Nhave a fun sports festival
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again. I can’t believe \NI’m actually able to take part
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in the sports festival without them finding out.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.87,0:16:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope nothing bad happens.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.24,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If the worst happens, \Na smoke signal will go up from the roof.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.48,0:16:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.95,0:16:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.10,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be an elaborately staged \Ncostumed demonstration for showmanship? {lit: for the sake of showup}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the times we live in...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.26,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Norimatsu Kintaro!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.38,0:17:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,His lackey, Red Pine! {??????? *** aka matsu}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.54,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, Black Pine!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yezo Spruce! {Yezo spruce (Picea jezoensis); Jezo spruce}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.56,0:17:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakhalin Fir! {Sakhalin fir (Abies sachalinensis)​}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.14,0:17:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,On the boss's wish, \Nthe Norimatsu Gang is here! {???????? ******* norimatsu... suisan = unannounced visit}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now drag Satoshi out here!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki and Satoshi are hiding.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, start the operation.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Alley-oop!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{Trying to be clever, huh?} Your clever tricks won't fool me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? {sore}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.72,0:17:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, where did you hide Satoshi? \NBe a good girl and tell us!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.33,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Pervert!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.61,0:18:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I'll have to crush all of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop ruining our festival already! {lit: don't be a hindrance anymore - meaning stop interrupting the festival}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.50,0:18:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Eh? What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.09,0:18:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.06,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.93,0:18:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.29,0:18:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.07,0:18:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is going too far.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.97,0:18:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop them!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll go tell them off myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.36,0:18:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let a single one escape! \NFind the real one!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.69,0:18:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Those are the skills \Nof {special-}makeup genius Sakazaki Yuji for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You...! Where's the real Satoshi?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.95,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.63,0:19:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.05,0:19:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Yuki? \NWhat's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.49,0:19:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even wearing \Nmy brand-new bra just for today!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Does it look good on me? {ANYTHING DOES, QUEEN}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.44,0:19:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My panties today are super-special too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.74,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, h-hold it now! \NH-Hold it, you hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I gotta try \Nto talk some sense into Kin-chan. {lit: settle it with words}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.17,0:19:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been good at running, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop that!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is between the two of us men! \NStay out of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.62,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've got you cornered!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.38,0:20:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kin-chan! That's going too far! Let's stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.94,0:20:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You're the one person \NI'll never let enjoy a sports festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of the past already! I...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.56,0:20:50.90,Top,,0,0,0,,I already forgot all about you pooping your pants \Nat the kindergarten sports festival!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're saying it again!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.76,0:21:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all Satoshi's fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.77,0:21:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You're the one who decided \Nto ruin the sports festival! You poopy pants!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.76,0:21:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that again, I dare you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.80,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}You poopy pants!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.80,0:21:11.92,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Why you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.92,0:21:15.00,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}You're a poopy pants, so what can I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.48,0:21:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.72,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.00,0:21:19.70,Top,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.01,0:21:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of exhausted.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.69,0:21:22.91,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Shut up, you poopy pants!{\i0} {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really have to go?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.17,0:21:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can't keep causing trouble \Nfor you any longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.87,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a messed up fate to carry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.46,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you are—\Na fateful transfer student? {??? sounds like a reference but idk }
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, go ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'm not looking!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.26,0:21:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.68,0:22:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Be well, folks!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.19,0:22:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'll ever stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.36,0:22:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yu— {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.74,0:22:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come back to me someday, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.04,0:22:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki's getting hungry!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.46,0:22:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Sir, one pork ramen, please! {tonkotsu ramen; pork bone broth ramen}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.50,0:22:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.72,0:22:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:48.03,0:22:49.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,Cappy.
Comment: 10,0:22:58.42,0:22:58.42,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 6,0:22:58.69,0:23:03.57,Song,,0,0,0,,{BECAUSE by ScooP; got full lyrics from EB's booklet: 見ようともしなかったことに\N君は今瞳を向け始めてる\N「ゴメンネ」とうつむいた君\N僕にはもう信じさせるものがない\N崩れそうなその肩を二度と\N僕は抱けない\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 離れて行く\N怖いなんて言葉にはつばを吐いてきた\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 小さくなる\Nあの頃は君の好きなもの すべて好きだったのに\N手に届く限りのもので\N君は今 幸せを創りあげたね\N夢を側に置きたい君\N夢だけはまだ追い続けていたい僕\N君はたぶん僕以外の男に\N抱かれるんだね\N君が思ってるより 僕は強くないさ\N誰も君の代わりできないから\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 振り向かない\N君の笑顔 今僕の瞳駆けめぐる\NBecause I miss you, Baby. もう見えない\N届かない僕の愛も夢もこの声さえも\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\N小さくなる\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\Nもう見えない}You're starting to turn your eyes
Dialogue: 6,0:23:04.70,0:23:13.18,Song,,0,0,0,,to something you never even tried to see
Dialogue: 6,0:23:14.08,0:23:18.84,Song,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry," you said, bowing your head
Dialogue: 6,0:23:19.80,0:23:28.71,Song,,0,0,0,,And I no longer had anything you could believe in
